<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tragedy-n">tragedy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'trædʒədi/    美 /'trædʒədi/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>悲剧性事件；惨案；不幸：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an air tragedy 
空难</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The tragedy of life is not so much what men suffer, but what they miss. 
生活的悲剧不在于人们受多少苦，而在于人们错过了什么。</p><footer>—— 卡莱尔</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(文学体裁) 悲剧；悲剧作品：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Shakespeare’s tragedy of Hamlet 
莎士比亚的悲剧《哈姆雷特》</p></div></div>